    "Name": "Ostsol",
    "Details": "Developed by Clan Sea Fox, this Ostsol carries fifteen double heat sinks. It uses a 300-rated engine to move at a top speed of 86 km/h. The side torso weapons are an ER Large Laser and an Improved Heavy medium laser. Two ER medium lasers are mounted in the center torso and cover the rear. All these weapons are tied into an advanced Targeting Computer. For protection, the Ostsol C carries nine tons of Reflective Armor.\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Quirk: Narrow/Low Profile</color></b>\n\n<b><color=#e62e00>Drop Cost Multiplier: 1.14</color></b>",
